<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
    />
    <meta
      http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"
      content="IE=edge"
    />
    <meta
      name="color-scheme"
      content="light dark"
    />
    <title>Email</title>
    <link
      rel="preconnect"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"
    />
    <link
      rel="preconnect"
      href="https://fonts.gstatic.com"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #033348;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
      color: white !important;
    "
  >
    <div
      class="inner-div"
      style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 600px; width: 90%"
    >
      <img
        class="mitt-arv-logo"
        style="
          height: 40px;
          max-width: 136.9px;
          width: 100%;
          margin-top: 20px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        "
        src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/mitt_arv_logo_horizontal.png"
        alt="Mitt Arv"
      />
      <div
        class="inner-div-bg-color"
        style="background-color: #043d55; padding: 2% 4%"
      >
        <div
          class="image-div"
          style="text-align: center"
        >
          <img
            class="alarm-ringing"
            style="
              display: inline-block;
              margin-top: 24px;
              margin-bottom: 24px;
              height: 60px;
            "
            src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/alaram_ringing.png"
            alt="Alaram"
          />
        </div>
        <h2
          style="
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            color: white;
          "
        >
          Greetings
        </h2>
        <h2
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
          "
        >
          Dear {{user_name}}!
        </h2>
        <p
          style="
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: white;
          "
        >
          This is your final reminder regarding the draft in your Emotional Will
          platform. Take this opportunity to finalize and save your draft,
          ensuring that your important thoughts and messages are preserved for
          the future.
        </p>
        <div
          class="progress-bar"
          style="height: 8px; background-color: white; border-radius: 40px"
        >
          <div
            class="progress"
            style="
              height: 8px;
              width: 100%;
              background-color: #d4545c;
              border-radius: 40px;
            "
          ></div>
        </div>
        <div style="height: 5px"></div>
        <table
          style="width: 100%; border-spacing: 0; border-collapse: collapse"
        >
          <tr>
            <td
              style="
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 0;
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                color: white;
              "
            >
              1 day remaining
            </td>
            <td
              style="
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-align: right;
                padding: 0;
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                color: white;
              "
            >
              out of 45 days
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <div
          class="time-sensitive-information"
          style="margin-top: 24px"
        >
          <p style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: white;">
            Urgent notice:
          </p>
          <ul
            style="
              font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
              font-size: 12px;
              padding-left: 20px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: white;
            "
          >
            <li style="color: white;">The draft you created 45 days ago will be deleted today.</li>
            <li style="color: white;">Once deleted, the content cannot be recovered.</li>
            <li style="color: white;">
              This deletion is in line with our 45-day draft lifespan policy.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; margin-block: 24px; color: white;">
          Please act immediately to save your valuable memories and expressions
          before they are lost.
        </p>
        <div
          class="time-sensitive-information"
          style="margin-top: 24px"
        >
          <p style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: white;">
            Immediate actions recommended:
          </p>
          <ul
            style="
              font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
              font-size: 12px;
              padding-left: 20px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: white;
            "
          >
            <li style="color: white;" >Log in now to review your draft</li>
            <li style="color: white;" >Save it as a final version if it's complete</li>
            <li style="color: white;" >
              If you need more time, copy the content and create a new draft
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p
          style="
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            color: white !important;
          "
        >
          Don't let your emotional legacy fade away. Take action now to preserve
          your thoughts and wishes.
        </p>
        <div style="height: 24px;"></div>
        <div
          class="center"
          style="
            margin: auto;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            width: 140px;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: #fd9320;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: flex;
          "
        >
          <a
            href="{{redirect_url}}"
            target="_blank"
            style="
              font-size: 12px;
              color: white;
              font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
              font-weight: 600;
              font-size: 12px;
              letter-spacing: 1.5%;
              margin: auto;
              text-decoration: none;
            "
          >
            View on Mitt Arv
          </a>
        </div>
        <p
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
          "
        >
          Warmest regards,<br />Team
          <span style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #84b5d2"
            >Mitt Arv</span
          ><br /><b>Zero - Life - Infinity</b>
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
          "
        >
          For any inquiries, kindly reach out to us
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
          "
        >
          at
          <a
            href="mailto:support@mittarv.com"
            style="color: white; text-decoration: none"
            onmouseover="this.style.color='#FD9320'"
            onmouseout="this.style.color='white'"
            >support@mittarv.com</a
          >
        </p>
        <div style="height: 32px"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="height: 56px"></div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
